summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5899 for the improvement of West 46th Street, from 6th Avenue Northwest to 9th Avenue Northwest; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; by constructing sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 77881, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
